parameterValues.DE:Prize Details:
Six night holiday to Hong Kong for two. The prize includes: 

•	Return economy class flights to Hong Kong International from London Heathrow, London Gatwick, Manchester or Dublin;
•	Return airport transfers;
•	Hotel transfers;
•	Three nights’ accommodation in Island Shangri-La Hotel based on two people sharing a Horizon Club Harbour View Room on a bed and breakfast basis; and 
•	Three nights’ accommodation in Kowloon Shangri-La Hotel based on two people sharing a Horizon Club Deluxe Harbour View Room on a bed and breakfast basis.

